---
title: Beef Rump in Garlic Parsley Butter with tender broccoli and mashed potato
description: The ubiquitous 'meat and two veg' gets a makeover in this take on a classic dish. The creamiest of mash and the most tender broccoli accompany cooked-to-perfection beef for a mouth-watering midweek treat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R01_W13_IE_IEXCCLB0004-2_Main_high-9e0ebc41.jpg
